    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年2月17日-2025年2月21日）",
    "followRuleId": "1209079877639213056",
    "content": "<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">各位商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本周共公示8条规则，生效9条规则，新增2条规则解读。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">具体内容如下，可点击查阅：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 20.0pt; line-height: 200%;\">一、【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.16%; background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">模块</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.78%; background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"36%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">规则名称</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.06%; background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">重点内容</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.16%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激励政策</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.78%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"36%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1209687396585705472&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">京东开放平台智能硬件类目招商激励政策（2025.2.6&mdash;2025.3.31</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">）</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.06%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">激励周期内，完成店铺开通并成功启用且保证新店铺经营时间不小于3个月的商家，若达成一定销售额并满足广告投放要求，将返还部分交易服务费。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.16%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">入驻</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.78%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"36%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1208967395511767040&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">关于新增《瑞士表/</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">德表准入品牌明细》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.06%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新增关于当前可入驻开店的瑞士表、德表类品牌明细清单。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.16%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">店铺管理</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.78%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"36%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1210107352817209344&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台店铺命名规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.06%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、新增品牌名称与企业商号重复场景的专卖店命名形式；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整店铺名称违反规则更名时的注意事项。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.16%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">营销</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.78%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"36%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1210102884314779648&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《2025</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">年京东开放平台3&middot;8</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">节活动规则》（注2.21</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">日生效）</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.06%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、明确活动节奏</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）活动预热期：2025年2月27日 00:00:00-2025年2月27日19:59:59</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（2）活动正式期：2025年2月27日 20:00:00-2025年3月8日23:59:59</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（3）招商时间：2025年2月15日12:00:00-2025年3月8日23:59:59</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、明确活动玩法</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）跨店满减：每满200元减30元</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（2）送礼专享折扣：85折</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（3）商品打标</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.16%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">结算</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.78%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"36%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1209676850964598784&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">关于新增《京东开放平台结算周期规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.06%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新增关于结算周期的各类场景与说明。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.16%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规管理</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.78%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"36%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1208722953223671808&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">个体合规管理规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.06%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">增加不当发布商品或信息中&ldquo;品牌错误使用&rdquo;的违规情形和处理措施 。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.16%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">纠纷</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.78%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"36%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1208689859091369984&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">个体纠纷处理规则》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.06%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">增加商家补充证据的时效要求。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 16.16%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"16%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">纠纷</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.78%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"36%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1208652768164843520&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">关于修订《京东开放平台运费问题纠纷处理标准》的公示通知</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 47.06%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"47%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">增加关于商家寄回地址产生运费争议问题的标准 。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、【规则生效】</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 45.82%; background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"45%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">规则名称</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 54.18%; background: #C00000; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"54%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">重点内容</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 45.82%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"45%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2614\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《京东开放平台招商资质标准细则》</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 54.18%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"54%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">在原有招商资质标准细则上新增注释，补充对于商标有效性、商标经营范围与品牌一致的要求。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 45.82%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"45%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=915123374395625472\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《京东开放平台&ldquo;0</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">元开店&rdquo;</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">试运营管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 54.18%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"54%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新增试运营状态的店铺最多可上架500商品（SPU）限制。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 45.82%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"45%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=833317602301448192\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《京东开放平台盲盒商品管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 54.18%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"54%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、品类范围扩展至全部品类；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、明确博彩类盲盒管理；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、更新违规处理规范；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、调整商品资质标准。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 45.82%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"45%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1207258240992284672\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《京东开放平台个人/</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">个体盲盒商品管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 54.18%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"54%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">包含商品发布规范、商品质量标准、违规处理措施等。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 45.82%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"45%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\"><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=562814072702242816&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《京东开放平台发票服务管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 54.18%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"54%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">增加开具虚假发票赔付的具体形式。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 45.82%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"45%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: l